fe inside a new clothing boutique by a Japan based clothing label.  My vanilla latte was pretty good. Looked like they have some interesting pastry options but had sold out by the time I was there (late afternoon).  Good option to get an espresso drink after the Latte shop down the street closes at 345 pm.  Clothes looked cool.  Very cool vibe.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cafe inside a new clothing boutique by a Japan based clothing label.  My vanilla latte was pretty good. Looked like they have some interesting pastry options but had sold out by the time I was there (late afternoon).  Good option to get an espresso drink after the Latte shop down the street closes at 345 pm.  Clothes looked cool.  Very cool vibe.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Realcelebetweets", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103096453549219536637/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-lLyGe7x6JfeU30GIaWlqt4Qf1mcViTQW6c-m2fIxckuv5yU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-21T14:00:20.945404015Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3MGRGQjVabmd5VWxKclJ6SlZPVk5JUTNJeGFHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3MGRGQjVabmd5VWxKclJ6SlZPVk5JUTNJeGFHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c710c45caa45:0xf9f659d014de60cf"}, {"name": "places/ChIJRapcxBDHwoARz2DeFNBZ9vk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25adGVFOUdSbU00UVVvNVJtdGFSbTlOY25oNGNGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A fancy new spot opened up on the main street in Little Tokyo, so I decided to check it out. I originally thought it was just a casual, mainstream kind of place, but the drink menu was surprisingly extensive and everything was seriously delicious. More than anything, the guy helping us was incredibly friendly, which made the whole experience amazing. If you’re ever in Little Tokyo, this is definitely a must-visit spot!!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A fancy new spot opened up on the main street in Little Tokyo, so I decided to check it out. I originally thought it was just a casual, mainstream kind of place, but the drink menu was surprisingly extensive and everything was seriously delicious. More than anything, the guy helping us was incredibly friendly, which made the whole experience amazing. If you’re ever in Little Tokyo, this is definitely a must-visit spot!!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Toru Matoba", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118270687089462240140/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-dfw6ZMtGKvmW8F23EqyG26ctLQODD79wTrn-5EUGp4GEKYo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-16T02:08:32.850652830Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25adGVFOUdSbU00UVVvNVJtdGFSbTlOY25oNGNGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25adGVFOUdSbU00UVVvNVJtdGFSbTlOY25oNGNGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c710c45caa45:0xf9f659d014de60cf"}, {"name": "places/ChIJRapcxBDHwoARz2DeFNBZ9vk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poUmVEbG5VRzV5VnpSS1NHMWtWbUZwUlcxM1gyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The barista was friendly and made the coffee sooo good! I ordered the butterscotch latte and it was amazing, I have a sweet tooth but it wasn’t too too sweet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The barista was friendly and made the coffee sooo good! I ordered the butterscotch latte and it was amazing, I have a sweet tooth but it wasn’t too too sweet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brandon LaRouche", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100165446300015173260/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3